  "description": "This is a close-up, overhead shot of a beach covered in dark, small pebbles. The pebbles vary in color \u2013 predominantly shades of gray, black, and brown, with occasional hints of reddish-brown and white. The texture appears rough and granular. Sunlight casts subtle shadows across the surface, creating a slightly rippled effect, as if from recent footprints or waves. The composition lacks a clear horizon or focal point, emphasizing the sheer density and pattern of the pebbles. Overall, it evokes a sense of natural, organic texture and a minimalist aesthetic.",
